==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪʒən|-ɪʒən]]

===Noun===
'''circumcision''' ([[circumcisions]])

# The act of [[amputating]] the [[foreskin]] or [[prepuce]] from the [[penis]].
# The act of amputating tissue from the [[vulva]] of the female.

====Related terms====
*[[circumcise]], [[circumcize]]
*[[female circumcision]]

